metadata.name: Trippy Pepe #1  #1/420
metadata.description:
Rare Editions of pepe art in the "Trippy Fan Art" Style

Not affiliated with Matt Furie or $Pepe. This is fan art and 
a community effort to make a memecoin more rare.

Every token minted represents the burning of 69,420 $Pepe.  

Within the generated traits are uncommon and rare traits, 
making certain tokens more rare than others... Those may be 
more valuable on secondary markets. Other than that, this 
token represents no more than the burning of a finite supply.

Total Supply: 420  
Mint Cost: 69,420 $PEPE + Eth (gas)  
Creator Royalties: 0%

100% of minted funds go to burn address: 
0x000000000000000000000000000000000000dEaD
